abstract: "A Ruby on Rails research artifact for studying human-in-the-loop governance in LLM-assisted algorithm implementation. The repository preserves prompt, result, error, correction, solver, fixture, and verification records across Traveling Salesman, Vehicle Routing, Assignment, and Max Flow implementations."
